## New Project: imprint
- **Replaces:** mitchellh/hashstructure (Go, 3,753 importers across v1+v2, 767 stars)
- **Why:** Archived July 2024, last release v2.0.2 May 2021. Single maintainer (mitchellh) no longer writing Go. gohugoio/hashstructure "blessed fork" has only 22 importers and 42 stars — negligible adoption. Pre-generics interface{} API, options struct not extensible, FormatV1/V2 versioning complexity, requires modifying types for Hashable/Includable interfaces.
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/imprint (verified available on pkg.go.dev)
- **Improvements:** generics Hash[T]/MustHash[T], functional options (no options struct), removed format versioning (V2 algo only), per-type custom hashers via WithTypeHasher, omitempty tag, simplified Hasher interface, compatibility layer
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #680 (scaffolding), #681 (core hash/walk), #682 (options/tags), #683 (compat layer), #684 (tests)

