## Watch List
| Package | Signal |
|---------|--------|
| mitchellh/go-ps (Go) | 877 importers, archived July 2024. Process listing. Platform-specific complexity. goss-org/go-ps fork exists. |
| PLY (Python) | 61.5M downloads/month, abandoned after 25 years. LALR parser generator — too complex to reimplement. Alternatives: lark, pyparsing, sly. |
| bleach (Python) | 52M downloads/month, deprecated Jan 2023. nh3 (Rust) is endorsed replacement but different API. |
| depd (Node) | 68M weekly, 7 years stale, Express dependency. Narrow scope. |
| python-jose (Python) | 2.7M weekly, unmaintained. PyJWT is recommended replacement (FastAPI adopted it). |
| julienschmidt/httprouter (Go) | Inactive maintenance. Go 1.22+ ServeMux and chi/gin/echo are alternatives. |

## Removed from Watch List
- certifi (Python): truststore is ecosystem-endorsed replacement.
- xeipuuv/gojsonschema (Go): google/jsonschema-go and santhosh-tekuri/jsonschema cover this.
- spf13/cast (Go): Actively maintained (v1.10.0 Sept 2025).
- go-ini/ini (Go): Already covered by stanza.
- colorama (Python): Already covered by chromapaint.
- minimist (Node): Alternatives exist (util.parseArgs, yargs-parser, mri).
- tabulate (Python): Actively maintained as of March 2026.
- patrickmn/go-cache (Go): Now stash project.
- fatih/structs (Go): Now structify project.
- mitchellh/copystructure (Go): Now replica project.
- mitchellh/hashstructure (Go): Now imprint project.
- Rust ecosystem: Most unmaintained crates have community forks.
- normalize-path (Node): Too trivial.
- gorilla/websocket (Go): coder/websocket is the established replacement.
- go-yaml (Go): yaml org fork (go.yaml.in/yaml/v3) is the maintained replacement.
- logrus (Go): Still maintained for security/bugs. slog/zerolog/zap are alternatives.
- mapstructure (Go): go-viper/mapstructure is the blessed fork.
- satori/go.uuid (Go): gofrs/uuid is the community fork.
- go-homedir (Go): os.UserHomeDir() in stdlib since Go 1.12.
- dustin/go-humanize (Go): Still receiving maintenance (commits in 2025).
- text-unidecode (Python): Unidecode is actively maintained alternative.
- mholt/archiver (Go): Replaced by mholt/archives by same author.
- nlopes/slack (Go): slack-go/slack is the maintained fork.
- pycparser (Python): Actively maintained, v3.0 Jan 2026.
- chardet (Python): Actively maintained, v7.1.0 March 2026.
- decorator (Python): Maintained, v5.2.1 Feb 2025.
- wrapt (Python): Maintained, v2.1.2 March 2026.
- oauthlib (Python): Actively maintained.
- imdario/mergo (Go): Moved to darccio/mergo, maintained.
- dgrijalva/jwt-go (Go): golang-jwt/jwt is dominant replacement.

